    SOURCED -->|auto-shortlist\nAI score meets threshold| SHORTLISTED
    SHORTLISTED -->|invite sent| CONTACT_REQUESTED
    CONTACT_REQUESTED -->|invite accepted| CONNECTED
    CONNECTED -->|first DM sent| MESSAGED
    MESSAGED -->|candidate replies| REPLIED
    REPLIED -->|recruiter moves| INTERVIEW
    INTERVIEW -->|recruiter moves| HIRED
    INTERVIEW -->|recruiter moves| REJECTED

    SOURCED -. recruiter .-> ARCHIVED
    SHORTLISTED -. recruiter .-> ARCHIVED
    CONTACT_REQUESTED -. invite timeout .-> ARCHIVED
    MESSAGED -. all followups exhausted .-> ARCHIVED
    REPLIED -. recruiter .-> ARCHIVED

